        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Avalúo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我梳理一下流转关系：Avalúo创建后先进入SinAsignar状态，然后经理分配给学院进入AsignadoColegio，学院代表再分配给专家进入AsignadoPerito。专家接受后才正式进入EnProgreso执行，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SinAsignar",
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "EnProgreso",
        "Manager assigns",
        "Colegio rep assigns",
        "Perito accepts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，专家接受是关键节点。之后专家提交工作进入EnRevision审核状态。这里有个分支：如果审核不通过，需要回到Observaciones待修改状态，专家修正后再回到EnProgreso；如果审核通过，则进入Completado完成状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EnProgreso",
        "EnRevision",
        "Observaciones",
        "Completado",
        "Work submitted",
        "Needs changes",
        "Perito fixes",
        "Approved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来绘制这个流程。从LabAnalyzer起始，经过SinAsignar、AsignadoColegio、AsignadoPerito、EnProgreso、EnRevision，分支到Observaciones形成循环，最终Completado归档到PatientRecords。双向箭头连接Observaciones和EnProgreso表示修正循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "SinAsignar",
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "EnProgreso",
        "EnRevision",
        "Observaciones",
        "Completado",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Observaciones到EnProgreso的箭头方向确认一下——是单向的，专家修正后重新进入进行中状态，不需要反向箭头。另外EnRevision到Completado的触发条件是Approved，这个标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
