      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下。Observaciones只指向EnProgreso，形成单向循环。EnRevision到Completado标注Approved。另外检查所有迁移标签：Avalúo created、Manager assigns、Colegio rep assigns、Perito accepts、Work submitted、Needs changes、Perito fixes、Approved都完整了。",
